co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.table
Interface Row

All Known Implementing Classes:
EmptyRow, Result
public interface Row

Represents one row in a table with a subset of columns. NOTE: Depending on the operation that returns Row as a result, it may contain all or just a subset of column values.
